Joanna P. Adler https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joanna_P._Adler 0 Joanna P. Adler (born 1964) is an American actress, known for her roles in Off-Broadway plays. She won an Obie Award in 1995. In 2014, Adler starred in the second season of the Lifetime television series Devious Maids. Joanna_P._Adler ( born 1964 ) is an_American_actress , known for her_roles in Off-Broadway plays .
